member.remarks:
Create a new user with the specified parameters. 
Required field is email or username.
Only a user with administrator rights can perform the operation.
Sample request:

    POST /users
    {
       "userBrief": 
       {
           "userName": "test",
           "email": "test@test",
           "tokenInfo" : {
                "token" : "1b0c7241b048a9c128c08de2574ef64f"
            }
        },
       "password": "test@test"
    }

Update user information. 
Only a user with administrator rights can perform the operation.
Sample request:

    PUT /users/:id
    {
       "userBrief": 
       {
           "tokenInfo" : {
                "token" : "1b0c7241b048a9c128c08de2574ef64f"
            }
        }
    }
